## What is Intentionally Missing

### Secrets
DATABASE_URL, REDIS_URL, DB_PASSWORD, and REDIS_AUTH_TOKEN
are not in the values files. These come from AWS Secrets
Manager via External Secrets Operator in Step 11. The
envFrom field in deployment.yaml is already there waiting.

### Pod Security Context
runAsNonRoot, readOnlyRootFilesystem, and
allowPrivilegeEscalation: false are not set yet. This is
Step 11 work alongside OPA Gatekeeper.

### NetworkPolicy egress tightening
Egress is currently open. Step 11 locks it down per service
so each pod can only reach what it needs — RDS, Redis, SQS,
or ECR depending on the service.

### Metrics server
HPA shows cpu: unknown because the metrics server is not
installed. This installs automatically in Step 10 with
kube-prometheus-stack.

