## Changes From the Initial Plan

### RBAC added — not in original plan
The original plan had no Role or RoleBinding templates.
Added during Step 7 after reviewing the security posture.
An explicit empty Role and RoleBinding on every service makes
the least-privilege decision auditable rather than implicit.

### terminationGracePeriodSeconds moved to values
Originally hardcoded at 30s in deployment.yaml. Changed to
a values field so data-ingestion can set 120s to match its
SQS visibility timeout without forking the template.

### values/ subfolder for environment values files
Originally the values files were going to sit at the chart
root. Moved into a values/ subfolder to keep the chart root
clean and make the structure easier to navigate as more
services are added.

### No .helmignore kept from scaffold
helm create generates a .helmignore file. Removed it — not
needed for this chart pattern since we are not packaging
and distributing the chart through a registry. ArgoCD reads
it directly from Git.

